'''Vweliu''' was a kind of [[Tree/Legends|tree]] from [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]]<ref name="FPtP">''[[From Pencil to Pixel: The Art of Star Wars Galaxies]]''</ref> that had a deep brown [[Wood/Legends|wood]] and were often made into desks.<ref name="ST">"[[Side Trip]]"</ref> The [[Vweilu nut|nut]] of the tree was edible and sometimes turned into a [[Candy/Legends|candy]].<ref name="RCTZ">''[[Republic Commando: Triple Zero]]''</ref>

